WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.350
Hey, good morning, family! I'm excited to

00:00:02.360 --> 00:00:04.030
be with you all today. I brought my best

00:00:04.040 --> 00:00:06.510
friend, Diana, on here—my wife.

00:00:06.520 --> 00:00:08.950
She's the behind-the-scenes person; she's

00:00:08.960 --> 00:00:11.270
been there answering the emails. I

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:13.629
brought her on before in a past video

00:00:13.639 --> 00:00:16.230
but never really let her talk a lot

00:00:16.240 --> 00:00:18.310
about our life and how we

00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:20.550
make things work. We get a lot

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:23.589
of emails from people saying,

00:00:23.599 --> 00:00:25.550
'My marriage is falling apart,''I'm in

00:00:25.560 --> 00:00:28.109
shambles here,'or 'My kids are

00:00:28.119 --> 00:00:30.109
backsliding or going to

00:00:30.119 --> 00:00:33.389
hell.'Email

00:00:33.399 --> 00:00:36.510
after email, and I feel in my

00:00:36.520 --> 00:00:39.750
heart it's time to talk about how

00:00:39.760 --> 00:00:42.069
to put God first place in your home.

00:00:42.079 --> 00:00:45.869
I can honestly tell you all,

00:00:45.879 --> 00:00:48.510
if you are not putting God first place

00:00:48.520 --> 00:00:50.110
in your house, you're not going to make

00:00:50.120 --> 00:00:52.110
it. There are nights you don't want to pray

00:00:52.120 --> 00:00:53.630
and you're just ready to go to

00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:55.869
bed, but you say, 'Hold on,

00:00:55.879 --> 00:00:58.270
this is priority.'I don't care

00:00:58.280 --> 00:01:00.509
how tired we are, we're going to pray and

00:01:00.519 --> 00:01:02.110
go before the Father for

00:01:02.120 --> 00:01:05.630
our children and seek Him.

00:01:05.640 --> 00:01:07.710
Even when we're dead tired, where you

00:01:07.720 --> 00:01:09.469
feel like you've worked all day

00:01:09.469 --> 00:01:09.479
and

00:01:09.479 --> 00:01:11.990
don't feel like doing this, how

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:15.190
bad is your 'want-to'? Do you want your

00:01:15.200 --> 00:01:17.830
children to know how to live by

00:01:17.840 --> 00:01:19.590
faith whenever they get older? Do you

00:01:19.600 --> 00:01:21.670
want your

00:01:21.680 --> 00:01:24.030
marriage to be strong?

00:01:24.799 --> 00:01:28.390
Putting God first, taking communion

00:01:28.390 --> 00:01:28.400
daily—we

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:30.550
take communion daily and pray

00:01:30.560 --> 00:01:33.710
together every day. We

00:01:33.720 --> 00:01:36.429
read our Bible and listen to the

00:01:36.439 --> 00:01:40.230
Word all the time. It's so much

00:01:40.240 --> 00:01:42.149
so that I don't even realize I

00:01:42.159 --> 00:01:44.270
do it. Even as the head of the house,

00:01:44.280 --> 00:01:46.230
I'm always continually praying,

00:01:46.240 --> 00:01:49.830
singing, or inviting Him into our

00:01:49.840 --> 00:01:52.149
home.

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:55.749
Being a leader, man, being a leader

00:01:55.759 --> 00:01:57.149
of your home,

00:02:03.159 --> 00:02:05.069
praying with your wife

00:02:05.069 --> 00:02:05.079
and

00:02:05.079 --> 00:02:06.789
your children before they go to bed,

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:09.229
anointing them with oil—doing the things

00:02:09.239 --> 00:02:10.949
you can do as a leader.

00:02:10.959 --> 00:02:14.750
They say 70 to 75%

00:02:14.760 --> 00:02:16.750
of all marriages with special needs

00:02:16.760 --> 00:02:21.030
children end in divorce, and 50% of

00:02:21.040 --> 00:02:23.070
all Body of Christ marriages end

00:02:23.070 --> 00:02:23.080
in

00:02:23.080 --> 00:02:26.030
divorce. Here we are, working together.

00:02:26.040 --> 00:02:28.910
Back whenever I got laid off at the

00:02:28.920 --> 00:02:31.790
church, I worked there for so long.

00:02:31.800 --> 00:02:33.309
When they came to me and

00:02:33.309 --> 00:02:33.319
said—because

00:02:33.319 --> 00:02:35.670
our pastor fell morally and

00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:37.229
they couldn't afford to keep a lot

00:02:37.239 --> 00:02:38.830
of the staff on—they eliminated a

00:02:38.840 --> 00:02:40.750
lot of things. So, we

00:02:40.760 --> 00:02:43.190
stepped out by faith and started doing

00:02:43.200 --> 00:02:45.869
our business selling online just

00:02:45.879 --> 00:02:47.430
seeking Him. The Lord said, 'Brandon,

00:02:47.440 --> 00:02:49.390
I'm going to speak to you every single

00:02:49.400 --> 00:02:51.630
day and show you things

00:02:51.630 --> 00:02:51.640
at

00:02:51.640 --> 00:02:53.270
thrift stores; I'm going to show you

00:02:53.280 --> 00:02:54.790
where to find

00:02:54.800 --> 00:02:58.509
provision for that

00:02:58.519 --> 00:03:01.229
day.'She

00:03:01.239 --> 00:03:04.190
quit her job because,

00:03:04.190 --> 00:03:04.200
as

00:03:04.200 --> 00:03:06.149
I said, she had a master's degree,

00:03:06.159 --> 00:03:09.750
finished with a 4.0 in college,

00:03:09.760 --> 00:03:12.509
and graduated top of the class summa

00:03:12.509 --> 00:03:12.519
cum laude.

00:03:12.519 --> 00:03:15.830
'Yeah, I graduated

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:21.430
from

00:03:21.430 --> 00:03:21.440
university

00:03:21.440 --> 00:03:23.990
while we had little kids. It was

00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:26.190
really

00:03:26.200 --> 00:03:29.229
a lot to do, but it

00:03:29.239 --> 00:03:31.869
was a way we were trying

00:03:31.879 --> 00:03:36.110
to find the path that God had for us.

00:03:36.120 --> 00:03:38.429
Then

00:03:38.439 --> 00:03:40.309
we

00:03:40.319 --> 00:03:43.470
started doing the thrift store thing, and

00:03:43.470 --> 00:03:43.480
that was

00:03:43.480 --> 00:03:45.110
the path that God

00:03:45.120 --> 00:03:48.149
blessed in our life. It was just

00:03:48.159 --> 00:03:50.110
going to a thrift store and finding

00:03:50.120 --> 00:03:51.869
stuff, and that was our provision for

00:03:51.879 --> 00:03:53.670
the day. I remember when it first

00:03:53.680 --> 00:03:56.990
started, the Lord gave me

00:03:57.000 --> 00:04:00.670
the idea. We didn't

00:04:00.680 --> 00:04:02.670
have enough money to last us through

00:04:02.680 --> 00:04:05.789
that month, and Brandon and I were

00:04:05.799 --> 00:04:07.030
talking about it. You were like, "It's the month of May and we

00:04:07.040 --> 00:04:08.110
don't have enough money

00:04:09.680 --> 00:04:11.030
to pay all our

00:04:11.040 --> 00:04:11.910
bills."So

00:04:11.920 --> 00:04:14.110
I went to God in prayer about it

00:04:14.120 --> 00:04:17.670
and asked

00:04:17.670 --> 00:04:17.680
for

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:19.789
a

00:04:19.799 --> 00:04:22.430
miracle or a creative idea.

00:04:22.440 --> 00:04:25.310
He brought to my mind the

00:04:25.310 --> 00:04:25.320
idea of

00:04:25.320 --> 00:04:26.870
finding

00:04:26.880 --> 00:04:28.749
something at a thrift store

00:04:28.759 --> 00:04:31.390
that would hold a profit

00:04:31.400 --> 00:04:33.550
and selling it online.

00:04:33.560 --> 00:04:35.749
The Lord really

00:04:35.759 --> 00:04:37.070
blessed that, and that's how we got through

00:04:37.080 --> 00:04:40.909
that month. The

00:04:40.909 --> 00:04:40.919
Lord

00:04:40.919 --> 00:04:42.950
just breathed on little things like that,

00:04:42.960 --> 00:04:45.189
and that's how we've

00:04:45.199 --> 00:04:47.629
lived our life: staying in

00:04:47.639 --> 00:04:50.790
prayer, taking communion every day.

00:04:50.800 --> 00:04:52.749
Whenever you stay rooted and grounded in

00:04:52.759 --> 00:04:55.990
God, He blesses

00:04:55.990 --> 00:04:56.000
you

00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:58.230
in the little areas.

00:04:58.240 --> 00:05:00.230
He's always

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:01.870
provided for us.

00:05:04.199 --> 00:05:06.350
If we have a problem or a need,

00:05:06.360 --> 00:05:08.590
we ask God what to do. We

00:05:08.590 --> 00:05:08.600
tell

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:10.590
Him

00:05:10.600 --> 00:05:13.909
we're at the end of our rope,

00:05:13.919 --> 00:05:15.870
and He's never early, He's never

00:05:15.870 --> 00:05:15.880
late—He

00:05:15.880 --> 00:05:17.670
always shows up right on time for

00:05:17.680 --> 00:05:20.150
us.

00:05:20.160 --> 00:05:23.029
Even in

00:05:23.029 --> 00:05:23.039
everything.'Yeah,

00:05:23.039 --> 00:05:24.749
it was that way even like what

00:05:24.759 --> 00:05:28.629
she was talking about in May.

00:05:28.639 --> 00:05:30.230
It was thousands of dollars we

00:05:30.240 --> 00:05:32.270
needed to pay our bills

00:05:32.280 --> 00:05:33.950
after I

00:05:33.950 --> 00:05:33.960
got

00:05:33.960 --> 00:05:35.790
laid off from the church. I

00:05:35.800 --> 00:05:38.309
thought, 'God, this isn't fair. How

00:05:38.319 --> 00:05:40.150
are we going to get through

00:05:40.150 --> 00:05:40.160
this?'You

00:05:40.160 --> 00:05:41.830
can feel sorry for

00:05:41.840 --> 00:05:43.870
yourself and whine,

00:05:43.880 --> 00:05:45.790
but that

00:05:45.790 --> 00:05:45.800
isn't

00:05:45.800 --> 00:05:47.909
going to get you anywhere. God is

00:05:47.919 --> 00:05:50.430
not moved by your need; He's moved by

00:05:50.440 --> 00:05:53.790
your faith and by a seed. When

00:05:53.800 --> 00:05:57.110
you have seedtime and harvest, when you

00:05:57.110 --> 00:05:57.120
sow,

00:05:57.120 --> 00:05:59.309
you'll reap. A lot of people think

00:05:59.309 --> 00:05:59.319
they're

00:05:59.319 --> 00:06:01.430
helpless

00:06:01.430 --> 00:06:01.440
and

00:06:01.440 --> 00:06:03.029
just sit back,

00:06:03.029 --> 00:06:03.039
but

00:06:03.039 --> 00:06:05.550
the Bible

00:06:05.560 --> 00:06:09.070
says whatever you put your hands to will

00:06:09.080 --> 00:06:11.870
prosper. He gives you the

00:06:11.880 --> 00:06:15.189
power to get wealth; He never told you

00:06:15.199 --> 00:06:17.430
to sit back and just let God do

00:06:17.440 --> 00:06:19.629
things. No, He gave you dominion and

00:06:19.639 --> 00:06:22.150
authority on this Earth. So,

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:24.790
we don't have a mailbox

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:27.390
mentality of looking for a

00:06:27.400 --> 00:06:29.830
handout. We

00:06:29.830 --> 00:06:29.840
don't say,

00:06:29.840 --> 00:06:32.309
'Lord, help us, we

00:06:32.319 --> 00:06:34.029
need a Holy Ghost handshake today at

00:06:34.039 --> 00:06:36.550
church; please somebody give us a

00:06:36.550 --> 00:06:36.560
hundred dollars.'I

00:06:36.560 --> 00:06:41.270
never one time

00:06:41.270 --> 00:06:41.280
sat

00:06:41.280 --> 00:06:43.390
there and whined about money

00:06:43.400 --> 00:06:45.950
because I realized what my

00:06:45.960 --> 00:06:48.589
Covenant says. He said

00:06:48.589 --> 00:06:48.599
He's

00:06:48.599 --> 00:06:50.230
never seen the righteous forsaken

00:06:50.240 --> 00:06:52.870
nor his seed begging bread. I said, 'Lord, if

00:06:52.880 --> 00:06:54.670
you said whatever I

00:06:54.680 --> 00:06:56.749
put my hands to would prosper and you

00:06:56.759 --> 00:06:59.029
give me creative ideas to get wealth,

00:06:59.039 --> 00:07:00.550
you're going to give it to

00:07:00.550 --> 00:07:00.560
us.'I

00:07:00.560 --> 00:07:02.110
was the

00:07:02.120 --> 00:07:03.710
one praying and fasting, and guess who

00:07:03.720 --> 00:07:05.589
He spoke to? My best friend.

00:07:06.759 --> 00:07:08.309
She came to me and

00:07:08.319 --> 00:07:11.950
said, 'Brandon, I have an

00:07:11.950 --> 00:07:11.960
idea,'and

00:07:11.960 --> 00:07:13.589
my response

00:07:13.599 --> 00:07:15.430
back was, 'That's crazy, that's not

00:07:15.440 --> 00:07:17.189
going to work.'But I felt like God

00:07:17.199 --> 00:07:20.469
told me this.

00:07:22.879 --> 00:07:24.990
When the Holy Spirit speaks

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:27.430
to you, it's that still, small voice.

00:07:29.919 --> 00:07:31.950
'I haven't had

00:07:31.960 --> 00:07:34.710
visitations like you, but I've always

00:07:34.720 --> 00:07:37.990
been led by

00:07:38.000 --> 00:07:39.950
that still, small voice of the Holy

00:07:39.960 --> 00:07:42.029
Spirit leading and guiding me.

00:07:42.039 --> 00:07:44.629
Even when my

00:07:44.639 --> 00:07:47.390
kids were

00:07:47.400 --> 00:07:49.550
born, we didn't have money

00:07:49.550 --> 00:07:49.560
to

00:07:49.560 --> 00:07:52.189
pay the hospital bills, and we

00:07:52.199 --> 00:07:55.350
would just believe God by faith that

00:07:55.350 --> 00:07:55.360
they

00:07:55.360 --> 00:07:57.149
would be paid.

00:07:57.159 --> 00:07:59.189
He

00:07:59.199 --> 00:08:00.909
always came through. He's

00:08:00.919 --> 00:08:02.869
never early, He's never late.

00:08:02.879 --> 00:08:05.149
Even in

00:08:05.149 --> 00:08:05.159
finding

00:08:05.159 --> 00:08:07.469
provision, I've

00:08:07.479 --> 00:08:10.469
always tried to be a Proverbs 31 wife,

00:08:10.469 --> 00:08:10.479
taking

00:08:10.479 --> 00:08:13.350
the resources we have

00:08:13.360 --> 00:08:15.149
and making them stretch as far as

00:08:15.159 --> 00:08:17.710
possible. I would go to garage sales

00:08:17.720 --> 00:08:20.390
for everything—baby blankets, baby

00:08:22.199 --> 00:08:24.029
bottles—just

00:08:26.919 --> 00:08:28.430
finding them used

00:08:28.440 --> 00:08:31.149
because God

00:08:31.159 --> 00:08:34.829
gives you resources. You

00:08:34.839 --> 00:08:37.670
don't just go buy everything new; you make

00:08:37.680 --> 00:08:39.990
it stretch as far as you

00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:41.829
can. If you're faithful

00:08:41.839 --> 00:08:43.469
with the little, He will make you

00:08:43.479 --> 00:08:46.110
ruler over much.

00:08:48.560 --> 00:08:51.389
We've lived

00:08:51.399 --> 00:08:55.190
so frugally, buying everything used

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:56.829
and going to garage sales.

00:09:04.600 --> 00:09:06.710
It's thinking, "How do I find the

00:09:06.720 --> 00:09:09.630
best deal? Lord, lead me to find

00:09:09.640 --> 00:09:12.870
that

00:09:12.870 --> 00:09:12.880
deal."He's

00:09:12.880 --> 00:09:14.790
always helped

00:09:16.430 --> 00:09:16.440
me.'But

00:09:18.920 --> 00:09:21.350
it was even

00:09:21.360 --> 00:09:22.790
whenever you came to me and

00:09:22.800 --> 00:09:25.829
told me the idea for selling

00:09:25.839 --> 00:09:27.910
online. I thought there was no way that

00:09:27.910 --> 00:09:27.920
was

00:09:27.920 --> 00:09:29.110
going to

00:09:29.110 --> 00:09:29.120
work,

00:09:29.120 --> 00:09:31.750
but I trusted

00:09:31.760 --> 00:09:33.470
the Holy Ghost inside

00:09:33.480 --> 00:09:35.190
of her just as much as she trusted the

00:09:35.200 --> 00:09:37.110
Holy Ghost inside of me.

00:09:39.279 --> 00:09:42.269
It took me humbling myself and

00:09:42.269 --> 00:09:42.279
saying,

00:09:42.279 --> 00:09:44.750
'Okay, I trust the voice of the

00:09:44.760 --> 00:09:46.910
Lord inside of you, babe. Let's

00:09:46.920 --> 00:09:48.430
try it. What do we have

00:09:48.430 --> 00:09:48.440
to lose?'So

00:09:48.440 --> 00:09:51.670
we had a hundred

00:09:51.670 --> 00:09:51.680
dollars and

00:09:51.680 --> 00:09:53.949
went to the thrift

00:09:53.959 --> 00:09:55.790
store. We bought the things the

00:09:55.800 --> 00:09:58.710
Lord put on our hearts to buy, and we

00:09:58.710 --> 00:09:58.720
were

00:09:58.720 --> 00:10:01.150
able to pay our

00:10:01.160 --> 00:10:04.310
electric bill. I said, 'Wow, it

00:10:04.320 --> 00:10:06.350
worked!'So

00:10:06.360 --> 00:10:08.949
I took another fifty dollars and bought more

00:10:11.640 --> 00:10:13.470
stuff.

00:10:13.480 --> 00:10:14.630
Every single time I

00:10:14.640 --> 00:10:17.870
pray, the Lord shows me

00:10:17.870 --> 00:10:17.880
a

00:10:17.880 --> 00:10:20.030
shirt or something in

00:10:20.040 --> 00:10:22.069
the thrift store. He would

00:10:22.079 --> 00:10:24.190
lead me and say, 'It's over off this

00:10:24.200 --> 00:10:26.389
street; go to this

00:10:26.389 --> 00:10:26.399
one.'I'd

00:10:26.399 --> 00:10:28.590
tell

00:10:28.590 --> 00:10:28.600
Diana,

00:10:28.600 --> 00:10:30.509
'Babe,

00:10:30.519 --> 00:10:32.150
I had a vision;

00:10:32.160 --> 00:10:33.829
if you go into this

00:10:33.839 --> 00:10:35.750
store, this shirt is in

00:10:35.750 --> 00:10:35.760
there.'I'd

00:10:35.760 --> 00:10:37.629
name the brand and what it looks like.

00:10:37.629 --> 00:10:37.639
She'd

00:10:37.639 --> 00:10:39.670
go in looking for the item and find it.

00:10:44.069 --> 00:10:44.079
We'd

00:10:48.839 --> 00:10:50.470
list it and sell it

00:10:50.480 --> 00:10:52.190
within a week, and we were able to pay

00:10:52.200 --> 00:10:54.310
our bills again. That's the way we've

00:10:54.320 --> 00:10:58.590
lived our life for

00:10:58.600 --> 00:11:01.430
seven years now—living by faith for every

00:11:01.440 --> 00:11:03.670
single thing and asking

00:11:03.680 --> 00:11:07.069
for favor. 'Lord, give us favor

00:11:07.079 --> 00:11:08.710
with the thrift store owners

00:11:08.710 --> 00:11:08.720
and

00:11:08.720 --> 00:11:10.910
favor at the

00:11:10.920 --> 00:11:12.790
garage sale today.'When we go

00:11:12.800 --> 00:11:13.870
through the garage sales, we go through the

00:11:13.880 --> 00:11:15.350
rich neighborhoods and ask the Lord

00:11:15.360 --> 00:11:17.910
where to go.

00:11:17.920 --> 00:11:20.430
You become desperate for

00:11:20.440 --> 00:11:22.670
hearing Him, and He will start speaking to

00:11:22.680 --> 00:11:25.829
you on a daily basis.

00:11:31.639 --> 00:11:33.750
Now we teach our

00:11:33.760 --> 00:11:35.990
kids how to live by faith

00:11:35.990 --> 00:11:36.000
and

00:11:36.000 --> 00:11:37.710
believe God.

00:11:37.720 --> 00:11:39.550
We believe

00:11:39.550 --> 00:11:39.560
with

00:11:39.560 --> 00:11:41.710
all our hearts that tithing and

00:11:41.710 --> 00:11:41.720
giving are

00:11:41.720 --> 00:11:44.990
for today. My life

00:11:45.000 --> 00:11:47.470
is an example of being at the bottom of

00:11:47.480 --> 00:11:49.269
the barrel and coming out on top.

00:11:59.320 --> 00:12:01.269
This year we didn't

00:12:01.279 --> 00:12:03.150
struggle like we did being janitors

00:12:03.160 --> 00:12:05.190
at the church,

00:12:05.200 --> 00:12:07.389
barely making it.

00:12:11.560 --> 00:12:14.230
There's so much

00:12:14.240 --> 00:12:16.310
financial stress today,

00:12:16.310 --> 00:12:16.320
but

00:12:16.320 --> 00:12:19.350
when you make God

00:12:19.350 --> 00:12:19.360
a

00:12:19.360 --> 00:12:22.230
priority,

00:12:22.240 --> 00:12:23.949
He makes you a priority.

00:12:23.959 --> 00:12:26.949
He is an

00:12:26.949 --> 00:12:26.959
ever-present

00:12:26.959 --> 00:12:29.269
help in a time of need.

00:12:29.269 --> 00:12:29.279
You've

00:12:29.279 --> 00:12:31.470
got

00:12:31.480 --> 00:12:33.870
to keep your marriage strong.

00:12:36.399 --> 00:12:38.470
You've got to

00:12:38.480 --> 00:12:41.269
make peace a priority in your home and

00:12:41.269 --> 00:12:41.279
keep

00:12:41.279 --> 00:12:44.030
strife out, because

00:12:44.040 --> 00:12:47.310
strife is a cancer. When

00:12:47.320 --> 00:12:49.310
you allow the enemy to come in through

00:12:49.320 --> 00:12:52.710
strife, it is a

00:12:52.720 --> 00:12:55.470
major blockage to financial

00:12:55.480 --> 00:12:58.350
overflow and

00:12:58.350 --> 00:12:58.360
the

00:12:58.360 --> 00:13:00.590
flow of the

00:13:00.600 --> 00:13:01.629
Holy

00:13:01.629 --> 00:13:01.639
Spirit.

00:13:01.639 --> 00:13:04.990
Make peace and joy the umpire

00:13:05.000 --> 00:13:07.310
of your life. The Bible says where

00:13:07.320 --> 00:13:10.030
there is strife, there is every evil work.

00:13:10.040 --> 00:13:11.829
We're not

00:13:11.839 --> 00:13:14.030
always perfect; I come across

00:13:14.040 --> 00:13:17.670
cranky some days.

00:13:31.760 --> 00:13:34.310
We're just

00:13:34.320 --> 00:13:37.790
human, but we have decided

00:13:37.800 --> 00:13:39.550
with all our

00:13:39.560 --> 00:13:42.230
hearts

00:13:42.240 --> 00:13:45.910
to make Jesus a priority and stand

00:13:45.920 --> 00:13:48.710
in the gap.

00:13:59.320 --> 00:14:01.230
Abraham said, 'I'm not

00:14:01.240 --> 00:14:02.749
going to let any man say he made me

00:14:02.759 --> 00:14:05.110
rich; only

00:14:05.110 --> 00:14:05.120
God.'God

00:14:05.120 --> 00:14:08.430
is our source

00:14:08.430 --> 00:14:08.440
and

00:14:08.440 --> 00:14:10.629
our provider;

00:14:10.639 --> 00:14:12.710
He's our Jehovah

00:14:12.710 --> 00:14:12.720
Jireh.

00:14:14.269 --> 00:14:14.279
We

00:14:14.279 --> 00:14:15.910
also

00:14:15.920 --> 00:14:18.110
started doing therapy

00:14:18.120 --> 00:14:19.870
dogs to help kids with special

00:14:19.880 --> 00:14:21.350
needs.

00:14:31.199 --> 00:14:33.470
It's a joy to see kids

00:14:33.480 --> 00:14:36.030
or elderly people

00:14:36.030 --> 00:14:36.040
get

00:14:36.040 --> 00:14:37.550
a dog.

00:14:44.440 --> 00:14:46.389
It's been a

00:14:46.399 --> 00:14:49.350
blessing working for

00:14:49.360 --> 00:14:52.470
yourself instead of 'working for the man.'God

00:14:52.470 --> 00:14:52.480
gives

00:14:52.480 --> 00:14:56.949
creative ideas.

00:15:02.120 --> 00:15:04.150
Being willing and obedient,

00:15:04.160 --> 00:15:06.749
you eat the good of the land.

00:15:08.480 --> 00:15:11.470
In both cases, the Lord spoke to her.

00:15:11.480 --> 00:15:13.990
She said, 'Brandon,

00:15:14.000 --> 00:15:15.310
this is what I believe the Lord has

00:15:15.310 --> 00:15:15.320
shown

00:15:15.320 --> 00:15:16.990
me,'and

00:15:17.000 --> 00:15:20.150
it's been big-picture things

00:15:20.150 --> 00:15:20.160
that

00:15:20.160 --> 00:15:22.069
changed the

00:15:22.079 --> 00:15:24.949
course of our

00:15:24.959 --> 00:15:28.150
lives.

00:15:29.880 --> 00:15:31.590
I'll get the small-picture things or

00:15:31.590 --> 00:15:31.600
visions of

00:15:31.600 --> 00:15:33.269
the

00:15:33.279 --> 00:15:35.949
future, but the

00:15:35.959 --> 00:15:38.309
Lord uses her in

00:15:38.309 --> 00:15:38.319
dreams

00:15:38.319 --> 00:15:40.550
to

00:15:40.560 --> 00:15:42.710
give her

00:15:42.710 --> 00:15:42.720
ideas.

00:15:42.720 --> 00:15:45.030
That's what

00:15:45.030 --> 00:15:45.040
it

00:15:45.040 --> 00:15:46.870
should be in a marriage; it's not

00:15:46.880 --> 00:15:49.749
a one-man show.

00:15:51.519 --> 00:15:53.309
You guys have to

00:15:53.319 --> 00:15:56.030
be a team. It's not, 'I'm the alpha male,

00:15:56.040 --> 00:15:59.350
hear me

00:15:59.350 --> 00:15:59.360
roar.'You

00:15:59.360 --> 00:16:02.350
are a covenant joint.

00:16:02.360 --> 00:16:04.189
If

00:16:05.829 --> 00:16:05.839
it's

00:16:07.629 --> 00:16:07.639
a

00:16:10.240 --> 00:16:12.710
one-man show,

00:16:12.720 --> 00:16:15.189
you're not going to win any games.

00:16:22.279 --> 00:16:25.189
Don't

00:16:32.000 --> 00:16:34.069
put God in a box. A

00:16:34.069 --> 00:16:34.079
lot

00:16:34.079 --> 00:16:36.990
of

00:16:36.990 --> 00:16:37.000
people

00:16:37.000 --> 00:16:38.870
feel like money can only come

00:16:38.880 --> 00:16:41.509
through a

00:16:43.519 --> 00:16:45.870
family member or

00:16:45.870 --> 00:16:45.880
a

00:16:45.880 --> 00:16:47.269
friend of the church.

00:16:52.800 --> 00:16:54.829
When you close yourself off like that,

00:16:56.279 --> 00:16:59.110
you're not open to hearing Him.

00:17:04.400 --> 00:17:07.230
He has no

00:17:07.240 --> 00:17:11.270
limits; He

00:17:11.280 --> 00:17:14.270
is infinite and mighty. He cares about

00:17:14.270 --> 00:17:14.280
the

00:17:14.280 --> 00:17:16.510
smallest

00:17:16.520 --> 00:17:18.990
needs.

00:17:28.439 --> 00:17:32.549
I've always said, 'God,

00:17:32.559 --> 00:17:36.190
I'm open to any way you

00:17:36.190 --> 00:17:36.200
choose to

00:17:36.200 --> 00:17:39.190
help

00:17:41.870 --> 00:17:41.880
us.'Usually,

00:17:44.360 --> 00:17:47.230
it's

00:17:47.240 --> 00:17:49.350
something we can use our hands to

00:17:49.360 --> 00:17:52.190
do

00:17:52.200 --> 00:17:54.110
because the Bible says He blesses

00:17:54.120 --> 00:17:56.390
the work of our hands.

00:18:01.720 --> 00:18:05.350
I

00:18:05.360 --> 00:18:08.029
journal to God and tell Him my desires.

00:18:08.039 --> 00:18:09.789
It's important

00:18:09.799 --> 00:18:11.630
to write down your prayer requests

00:18:17.480 --> 00:18:19.350
because if you only

00:18:19.360 --> 00:18:20.830
think about the big things,

00:18:20.840 --> 00:18:23.390
you won't notice

00:18:23.400 --> 00:18:25.630
that He's been there

00:18:25.630 --> 00:18:25.640
answering

00:18:25.640 --> 00:18:27.470
a hundred small

00:18:27.480 --> 00:18:29.390
prayers

00:18:29.400 --> 00:18:30.990
throughout

00:18:31.000 --> 00:18:33.750
the

00:18:36.070 --> 00:18:36.080
year—like

00:18:38.270 --> 00:18:38.280
a

00:18:40.559 --> 00:18:42.630
new pair of sneakers

00:18:42.640 --> 00:18:45.630
or

00:18:45.630 --> 00:18:45.640
losing

00:18:45.640 --> 00:18:49.350
ten

00:18:49.360 --> 00:18:51.510
pounds.

00:18:53.880 --> 00:18:56.270
If

00:18:56.280 --> 00:18:58.870
you don't write it down, you'll miss it.

00:19:25.840 --> 00:19:28.029
Every year

00:19:28.039 --> 00:19:31.510
in January, we set out a

00:19:31.520 --> 00:19:33.510
list

00:19:33.510 --> 00:19:33.520
of

00:19:33.520 --> 00:19:35.590
what we're believing

00:19:35.600 --> 00:19:39.789
God for.

00:19:43.320 --> 00:19:44.710
It could be

00:19:44.710 --> 00:19:44.720
a

00:19:44.720 --> 00:19:47.430
vacation

00:19:49.310 --> 00:19:49.320
or

00:19:51.440 --> 00:19:54.230
a

00:19:56.669 --> 00:19:56.679
house.

00:19:59.400 --> 00:20:01.630
We push as

00:20:01.640 --> 00:20:04.070
hard as we can to believe for that.

00:20:10.360 --> 00:20:12.149
We put Megan on the

00:20:12.159 --> 00:20:14.510
list every year—for her to be

00:20:14.520 --> 00:20:17.310
completely whole

00:20:19.039 --> 00:20:21.190
and

00:20:23.200 --> 00:20:24.990
restored.

00:20:25.000 --> 00:20:27.029
We even put

00:20:27.039 --> 00:20:28.710
down for her to be potty trained;

00:20:28.720 --> 00:20:30.870
she's getting there,

00:20:30.870 --> 00:20:30.880
though she

00:20:30.880 --> 00:20:32.990
still

00:20:32.990 --> 00:20:33.000
has

00:20:33.000 --> 00:20:35.230
accidents.

00:20:35.230 --> 00:20:35.240
We

00:20:35.240 --> 00:20:38.149
look at where we came from.

00:20:40.320 --> 00:20:41.470
We're believing

00:20:52.159 --> 00:20:54.190
for a new house

00:20:54.200 --> 00:20:55.950
right now

00:20:58.880 --> 00:21:01.029
that's bigger

00:21:01.029 --> 00:21:01.039
and

00:21:01.039 --> 00:21:03.909
has

00:21:03.919 --> 00:21:05.669
a

00:21:05.679 --> 00:21:07.750
special room for

00:21:07.750 --> 00:21:07.760
Megan.

00:21:07.760 --> 00:21:10.630
Write

00:21:10.640 --> 00:21:13.149
it down at the beginning of the year.

00:21:13.159 --> 00:21:15.029
For your marriage, thank Him

00:21:15.029 --> 00:21:15.039
that

00:21:15.039 --> 00:21:16.390
it

00:21:16.390 --> 00:21:16.400
will

00:21:16.400 --> 00:21:18.510
be stronger at the

00:21:18.520 --> 00:21:20.230
end of the year.

00:21:29.320 --> 00:21:32.390
If you're single and

00:21:32.400 --> 00:21:35.110
believing for a godly spouse,

00:21:37.840 --> 00:21:39.990
write down the

00:21:43.480 --> 00:21:45.430
characteristics and qualities.

00:21:45.440 --> 00:21:47.310
Brandon and I both did

00:21:47.310 --> 00:21:47.320
that

00:21:47.320 --> 00:21:49.230
before we ever met.

00:21:49.240 --> 00:21:51.269
I was

00:21:51.269 --> 00:21:51.279
thirteen

00:21:51.279 --> 00:21:53.669
when I wrote it down.

00:21:58.200 --> 00:22:00.510
I would pray

00:22:00.520 --> 00:22:02.710
over him before I even knew who he

00:22:02.710 --> 00:22:02.720
was—praying that God

00:22:02.720 --> 00:22:04.630
would keep him

00:22:04.640 --> 00:22:08.350
pure

00:22:10.789 --> 00:22:10.799
and

00:22:13.520 --> 00:22:16.269
on fire for

00:22:16.279 --> 00:22:18.230
Him.

00:22:33.559 --> 00:22:35.630
I

00:22:35.640 --> 00:22:37.909
strongly believe the protection I've had in my life

00:22:41.600 --> 00:22:43.310
was

00:22:45.360 --> 00:22:47.430
because he prayed over me before he

00:22:47.440 --> 00:22:49.990
ever met me.

00:22:54.799 --> 00:22:57.350
After we got married, we showed

00:22:57.360 --> 00:22:59.590
each other our

00:23:01.669 --> 00:23:01.679
lists.

00:23:03.960 --> 00:23:06.310
I wrote

00:23:06.320 --> 00:23:09.430
down the personality type

00:23:09.430 --> 00:23:09.440
and

00:23:10.950 --> 00:23:10.960
everything.

00:23:10.960 --> 00:23:13.470
I

00:23:13.480 --> 00:23:15.430
said,

00:23:21.080 --> 00:23:22.549
'Father, I'm

00:23:22.559 --> 00:23:24.110
not settling for

00:23:24.120 --> 00:23:26.710
an

00:23:26.710 --> 00:23:26.720
Ishmael.

00:23:26.720 --> 00:23:28.990
I want my

00:23:28.990 --> 00:23:29.000
Isaac.'Interestingly,

00:23:29.000 --> 00:23:31.669
my

00:23:31.679 --> 00:23:33.789
parents

00:23:33.799 --> 00:23:38.110
felt

00:23:38.120 --> 00:23:40.230
called to move to Fort

00:23:40.230 --> 00:23:40.240
Worth,

00:23:40.240 --> 00:23:43.750
Texas, to go to Bible school, and that's where

00:23:57.720 --> 00:23:59.750
I met her.

00:24:06.159 --> 00:24:07.830
The footsteps of the righteous are

00:24:07.840 --> 00:24:10.750
ordered by the Lord.

00:24:34.840 --> 00:24:37.350
If it wasn't for

00:24:37.360 --> 00:24:39.190
keeping God a priority,

00:24:39.200 --> 00:24:40.789
we would have been divorced a long

00:24:40.799 --> 00:24:43.310
time ago.

00:24:43.320 --> 00:24:45.909
It hasn't always been easy, but we are quick to repent. If I have

00:24:55.919 --> 00:24:57.830
a

00:24:57.840 --> 00:24:59.990
bad

00:24:59.990 --> 00:25:00.000
attitude,

00:25:00.000 --> 00:25:01.870
I

00:25:01.880 --> 00:25:03.710
say, 'I'm sorry.'I want to

00:25:03.720 --> 00:25:06.350
have a soft heart.

00:25:11.640 --> 00:25:13.669
The Holy Spirit will rebuke me

00:25:13.669 --> 00:25:13.679
and

00:25:13.679 --> 00:25:15.750
say,

00:25:15.760 --> 00:25:17.149
'You need to go back and make that

00:25:19.389 --> 00:25:19.399
right.'He's

00:25:21.039 --> 00:25:23.230
always got her back.

00:25:27.799 --> 00:25:30.230
I'll go to her and say, 'Babe,

00:25:30.240 --> 00:25:31.669
the Holy Spirit just corrected me on how

00:25:31.679 --> 00:25:34.149
I

00:25:34.149 --> 00:25:34.159
talked

00:25:34.159 --> 00:25:36.950
to

00:25:36.950 --> 00:25:36.960
you,

00:25:36.960 --> 00:25:38.470
and

00:25:38.470 --> 00:25:38.480
I

00:25:38.480 --> 00:25:40.310
apologize.'She's

00:25:40.320 --> 00:25:42.510
glad

00:25:42.520 --> 00:25:44.630
He cares about her like that.

00:25:47.279 --> 00:25:48.510
Let

00:25:52.000 --> 00:25:54.389
the Lord be the captain of

00:25:54.399 --> 00:25:56.830
your life. You drive the car, but let Him be the

00:26:03.799 --> 00:26:05.710
pilot.

00:26:15.120 --> 00:26:18.230
I

00:26:18.240 --> 00:26:21.029
refuse to let my

00:26:21.039 --> 00:26:23.510
intellect lead me because the

00:26:23.510 --> 00:26:23.520
carnal

00:26:23.520 --> 00:26:25.630
man knows not the things of the

00:26:25.640 --> 00:26:28.470
Lord. I want to be

00:26:28.470 --> 00:26:28.480
controlled

00:26:28.480 --> 00:26:30.590
by the Holy Spirit.

00:26:40.720 --> 00:26:44.149
He

00:26:44.159 --> 00:26:47.110
will make every path

00:26:47.120 --> 00:26:49.830
straight.

00:26:51.520 --> 00:26:53.870
We don't have enough time on this

00:26:53.880 --> 00:26:56.630
Earth to keep making bad

00:26:56.640 --> 00:26:58.909
choices.

00:27:00.600 --> 00:27:03.870
Every

00:27:03.880 --> 00:27:05.909
day

00:27:11.669 --> 00:27:11.679
counts.

00:27:19.640 --> 00:27:22.510
Intellect and

00:27:22.520 --> 00:27:25.430
thinking you know the way

00:27:25.440 --> 00:27:27.350
can get you in trouble.

00:27:34.360 --> 00:27:36.830
Knowledge sometimes gets in

00:27:36.840 --> 00:27:39.870
the way because you feel like you

00:27:39.870 --> 00:27:39.880
don't

00:27:39.880 --> 00:27:42.110
need Him.

00:27:45.960 --> 00:27:48.269
That's when things don't work.

00:28:02.120 --> 00:28:04.549
We just wanted to come on

00:28:04.549 --> 00:28:04.559
today

00:28:04.559 --> 00:28:07.909
and

00:28:07.909 --> 00:28:07.919
be

00:28:07.919 --> 00:28:09.470
real about marriage.

00:28:20.840 --> 00:28:24.430
I hope this

00:28:24.440 --> 00:28:26.870
blessed you.

00:28:26.880 --> 00:28:29.190
Father, we thank you

00:28:29.190 --> 00:28:29.200
for

00:28:29.200 --> 00:28:30.710
every married couple

00:28:30.720 --> 00:28:32.909
watching this. We pray

00:28:32.909 --> 00:28:32.919
a

00:28:32.919 --> 00:28:35.269
blessing over their marriage.

00:28:37.159 --> 00:28:39.310
No weapon formed against

00:28:39.320 --> 00:28:41.549
them shall prosper. Satan, we take

00:28:41.559 --> 00:28:43.350
authority over you in the name

00:28:43.360 --> 00:28:45.950
of Jesus and bind you off

00:28:45.960 --> 00:28:49.070
their homes

00:28:49.080 --> 00:28:50.990
and

00:28:51.000 --> 00:28:53.230
finances.

00:28:53.240 --> 00:28:55.350
Get off their

00:28:55.360 --> 00:28:58.310
children!

00:29:11.279 --> 00:29:13.630
We are

00:29:13.640 --> 00:29:15.789
seated with Jesus Christ

00:29:15.799 --> 00:29:18.549
in

00:29:18.559 --> 00:29:20.870
heavenly

00:29:20.880 --> 00:29:24.190
places.

00:29:24.200 --> 00:29:26.870
We command

00:29:26.870 --> 00:29:26.880
you

00:29:26.880 --> 00:29:29.830
to bow your knee and get out of

00:29:29.840 --> 00:29:32.549
our houses.

00:29:37.880 --> 00:29:40.350
We call for healing and wholeness.

00:29:40.360 --> 00:29:42.789
If

00:29:45.110 --> 00:29:45.120
a

00:29:47.720 --> 00:29:51.029
marriage

00:29:51.039 --> 00:29:53.149
is in jeopardy, we pray peace and

00:29:53.159 --> 00:29:54.669
deliverance.

00:29:57.120 --> 00:29:59.470
You

00:30:04.110 --> 00:30:04.120
are

00:30:07.880 --> 00:30:09.310
the

00:30:09.320 --> 00:30:11.990
restorer of all things. We call

00:30:12.000 --> 00:30:13.990
the

00:30:14.000 --> 00:30:15.870
children

00:30:15.880 --> 00:30:18.389
home in

00:30:25.470 --> 00:30:25.480
Jesus'name.

00:30:32.919 --> 00:30:34.950
We take our covenant rights.

00:30:34.950 --> 00:30:34.960
We

00:30:34.960 --> 00:30:37.269
are

00:30:37.279 --> 00:30:38.950
so

00:30:38.960 --> 00:30:40.830
grateful for everything You did

00:30:40.840 --> 00:30:43.230
on that cross.

00:30:43.230 --> 00:30:43.240
I

00:30:45.230 --> 00:30:45.240
speak

00:30:45.240 --> 00:30:47.190
to

00:30:47.200 --> 00:30:49.310
